). Along with the detailed PSD analysis, we also\npresent the results of our extended (1998-2015) intra-night optical monitoring\nprogram and newly acquired optical photo-polarimetric data for the source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2017 16:38:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Mar 2017 15:08:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-22"}
