isotropy generated by quantum fluctuation during inflation, and CMB B-mode\npolarization would be observed differently from the standard predictions by\ngeneral relativity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2017 18:20:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Oct 2017 08:42:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-08"}
