osities, a large fraction of\nFSRQs shows signs of thermal emission from the accretion disc, contributing in\nthe optical-UV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2017 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2017 09:41:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-31"}
