rared wavelength range, including the\ndisk's rim, accretion arms and potentially the expected circumstellar disks\naround each of the binary components.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2017 15:40:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2017 13:37:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
